data.description: Welcome home! NO HOA! As soon as you walk in the front door you are greeted with an open living space and high ceilings. The kitchen over looks living room and has an eat in space with tons of natural lighting! With this split floor plan you have a sense of privacy from guests or other family members. The master bathroom features a large soaker tub and walk in shower. On the other side of the home you have two identical secondary bedrooms and a shared bathroom. This home is ready for its new owners, make an appointment today!
